# --- Remote IMAP account ---
IMAPAccount mxroute
Host moose.mxrouting.net
Port 993
User suraj@bugswriter.com
PassCmd "pass accounts/mail"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

# --- Remote Store ---
IMAPStore mxroute-remote
Account mxroute

# --- Local Maildir Store ---
MaildirStore mxroute-local
Path ~/mail/
Inbox ~/mail/Inbox/
SubFolders Verbatim
Flatten .

# --- Sync Channel ---
Channel mxroute
Far :mxroute-remote:
Near :mxroute-local:
Create Near
SyncState *
Sync All
Expunge Both
Remove Both
